      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee iṣgahje Deenas-Widdû. Bet Ben-Adads pee-dsehrahs Teltis ar teem trihsdef-mits un diwi Kehnizeem / kas tam par Paliggeim bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad iṣgahje to Semmes-Waldneeku Puſchi papreekschu. Tad iṣfuhttja Ben-Adads / un tee stahstija tam/ un fazzija: No Samarijas irr Wiḣri iṣgahjuscht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiṅsch : Sa-grahbeet tohs dshiwus/ lai tee irr Meera pehz lat Raunchanas pehz iṣgahjuscht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu ſchee Semmes-Waldneeku Puſcht no Piilsfah-ta bija iṣgahjuscht ar to Speh-ku/ kas teem pakkat gahje/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad kawe ikweens to / kas winnam preckcha nahze. Un tee Sihreti behdse/ un Israëls dsinnahs teem pakkat. Bet Ben-Adads tas Kehniisch no Sihri-jas iṣglahbahs us weenn Sir-gu/ un ar Jahtneekeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Israëta Kehniisch iṣgahje / un kawe Sirgus un Rattus/ ta kawe wiṅsch tohs Sthreus ar leelu Raunchanut.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nahze tas Praweets pee to Israëta Kehnizu/ un fazzija us to : Eij/ stiprtinajees/ neim wehrā/ un uhko/ ko tu darri/ jo zitta Gaddā nahkstas Kehniisch no Sihrijas atkat pretti tew.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ta Kehnizra no Sihri-jas Kalpt bij us to fazzijſcht: Winnu Deewi irr Kalna-Dee wi/ tapehz irr tee stipraki ne ka\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz darri ſcho Leet Atxetmu tohs Kehnizus/ itka ru no ſawas Weetas/ nn eeze Leelus-Kungus winnu Weeta\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un taiſi tew weenu Ka-ra-Spehku/ ka tas bija/ kas te suddis/ un Sirgus/ ka win Sirgi / un Rattus / ka win Ratti/ un lai mehs ar teem Kl junk kaujamess/ ko ſinn / mehs tohs ne peewarrefim? wiṅsch klaustija winnu Balsin un darrija ta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un zittā Gaddā taiſ Ben-Adads tohs Sthreus/ zehlehs uhs Aweku/ prett Isrelu karroht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee Israëta Beh tappe arri lihdsmati/ un avgadajhs ar Barribu / un ga-teem pretti/ un Israëta Behapmettehs teem itt pretti/ itt ka diwi Kasu Pulki/ bet to Si-reu bija wiﬀa ta Semne pi\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas Deewa Wi-atgahje/ un runnaja us to Isreta Kehnizu / un fazzija: faſka tas KUNGS: Tapehz tee Sihreti irr fazzijſchi / tKUNGS irr weens Deews Kasnu/ un ne arrt weens Deeto Geleijn/ tad efinn es ſcho lu Pulku tawa Rohka dewts/juhs atsihstat man effain KUNGSU.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ſchee bij teem zittepre\n"
    }
  ],
